RT @BrianLehrer: ICYMI catch @propublica's @CarolineYLChen on the COVID-19 vaccine's eventual distribution:

https://t.co/MgodNMoetd

RT @CurtisSChin: Pause this #ThanskgivingWeek to read this: 
The Enraging Deja Vu of a Third Coronavirus Wave https://t.co/j7qH3v3Qdh @Caro…

My office chair has been taken over by my cat, which means... I’m taking a break! 

TBH I’m emotionally exhausted from #Covid reporting since Feb & need to not look at case counts for a bit. I’ll be back after Thanksgiving, ready to talk vaccines & more.

Take care, everyone! https://t.co/fVmspzK2ss

My latest: Health care workers don’t need patronizing praise. They need resources, federal support, and for us to stay healthy and out of their hospitals.

The Enraging Deja Vu of A Third Coronavirus Wave
https://t.co/0iN8taDMhl

Some quick thoughts re: #Pfizer #vaccine news: 
- Far better results than expected
- So far just a press release, eager to see data
- Want to see: results in elderly, impact on *severe* #COVID19
- Looking forward to FDA adcomm
- Overall: cautiously optimistic!
